data.description: Start your New Year with this great home in the heart of Madisonville. You will enjoy a one-level floor plan that has three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, the home also has a single car garage with a screened in porch for entertaining. Walk across your large level lot to utilize your large 35 foot long carport. Next to your carport you will enjoy a full block outbuilding with electric. This home has so much to offer and is less than a minute from downtown Madisonville.
